*coriander-1.0.0 (10 Oct 2004); Pieter Van den Abeele <pvdabeel@gentoo.org>

  10 Oct 2004; Stewart Allen <srallen@mweb.co.za> coriander-1.0.0.ebuild:
  Coriander is a Linux graphical user interface (GUI) that let you control a 
  Digital Camera through the IEEE1394 bus. Added ~x86 to KEYWORDS.
  Changed ">=media-plugins/libdc1394-1.0.0" in DEPEND. 
  Version Bump.

  05 Sep 2004; Sven Wegener <swegener@gentoo.org> :
  Fixed ChangeLog header.

*coriander-1.0.0_pre3 (09 Aug 2004)

  09 Aug 2004; Pieter Van den Abeele <pvdabeel@gentoo.org> coriander-1.0.0_pre3.ebuild:
  provides v4l compatibility for Apple iSight under linux 

